[h1]What is it[/h1]
[b]Talon voice[/b] is microphone voice command system. It lets you say for example "spawn crate" to spawn a crate prop. This is mostly useful for VR but can also be a roleplay element: You can easily program it to react to for example [i][url=https://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Muggles%27_Guide_to_Harry_Potter/Magic/Avada_Kedavra]avada kedavra[/url][/i]

[hr]


[h1]Supported commands[/h1]
See Github [url=https://github.com/Metastruct/talon_gmod#voice-commands]command list[/url]

[h1]Required components[/h1]
- [b]Talon Voice application[/b] (FREE and Open Source). [b]Install from[/b] https://talonvoice.com/
- Microphone
- This workshop addon to communicate with GMod

[h1]CONTRIBUTE / BUG REPORTS / ISSUES[/h1]
You can contribute to the addon (and log bugs) [url=https://github.com/Metastruct/talon_gmod/issues]here[/url].
This is trying to be formed into a base for everyone to build upon.

